title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Relapse
description:
The ideal park and street board for anyone committed to or coming back to camber-based riding. The Relapse brings together massive amounts of power and durability with the snap, response, and feel of traditional camber.
To learn more about the Relapse visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/relapse/
